	<div id='content'>
	
		<div id='overview'>
		
		<p class='intro'>
			 Footprint is a tool that gives web designers and developers what they need to track projects and communicate
			 effectively with their clients.
		</p>
		
		<p class='intro'>
			From the initial concept right through to the end result, Footprint
			provides simple, easy to use tools that help designers manage their projects.
			Have a look at <a href='/features'>the features page</a> to find out more.
		</p>
		
		<div class='featurePreview'><img src='/media/images/features/clients.jpg' alt='Client Feature Preview' /></div>
		<h3>Manage your clients online</h3>
		
		<p>
			Store your client base within Footprint and take advantage of the useful tools that can help you
			get your projects done on time.
		</p>
		
		<div class='clear'><br /></div>
		<div class='featurePreview'><img src='/media/images/features/tasks.jpg' alt='New Tasks Feature Preview' /></div>
		<h3>Take control of your projects</h3>
		
		<p>
			Store all your project information in one place. The Footprint dashboard lets you keep an eye on
			what's been recently changed and on any new client requests.
		</p>
		
		<div class='clear'><br /></div>
		<div class='featurePreview'><img src='/media/images/features/tasksList.jpg' alt='Tasks Feature Preview' /></div>
		<h3>See your tasks at a glance</h3>
		
		<p>
			The task view lets you communicate with your client, view comments, documents and screenshots all
			from the one screen.
		</p>
		
		<div class='clear'><br /></div>
		<div class='featurePreview'><img src='/media/images/features/comments.jpg' alt='Comments Feature Preview' /></div>
		<h3>Collaborate on everything</h3>
		
		<p>
			The comments feature links into all other areas of Footprint which keeps your client in the loop.
			Collaborate on current projects, screenshots, documents or tasks.
		</p>
		
		<div class='clear'><br /></div>
		<div class='featurePreview'><img src='/media/images/features/screenshot.jpg' alt='Screenshot Feature Preview' /></div>
		<h3>Track design changes with ease</h3>
		
		<p>
			With simple version control on all types of graphics, Footprint makes it easy to track changes in the
			same design whilst keeping things easy to use and clutter free.
		</p>
		
		<div class='clear'><br /></div>
		<div class='featurePreview'><img src='/media/images/features/documents.jpg' alt='Document Storage Feature Preview' /></div>
		<h3>Share your project documents</h3>
		
		<p>
			Store your project documents online while keeping them current. It's perfect for designs,
			zip files, project specs and any other deliverable. Version control included.
		</p>
		
